":1541161,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06dbe318f627ff4647fa4e96ad4daafdc7fedd3","tid":1541161,"uid":82145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:03.000Z","msg":"全世界都以為我地爭取成功<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人權法</span>會唔會就咁算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國文宣巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩幫到手都幫<br />\n因為9月8先係終極一戰<br />\n唔可以比林奠咁就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"屌你，一堆人喺twitter搏命你喺度喊驚？<br />\n<br />\n講咁多做乜鳩，上twitter做文攻啦！"},{"pid":"d8785b79858cdfcd044b9524f353b297e219e4d2","tid":1541161,"uid":249705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下星期一 9月9 大專罷課集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為大專生<br />\n今次開學罷課搞到咁柒<br />\n完全俾中學生比下去<br />\n知道大家好慚愧 好想付出更多<br />\n<br />\n短時間內嘅主題<br />\n係要美國國會通過香港人權法案<br />\n既然7號有塞機場 8號有美國領事館<br />\n點解我哋大專生<br />\n唔襯中學生9號一週一罷<br />\n一齊搞多次罷課集會<br />\n有聲勢浩大既民意表態<br />\n既可以團聚學界<br />\n又為之後嘅三罷打強心針<br />\n<br />\n7號8號9號 一連三日嘅大型示威集會<br />\n就可以show到民意支持<br />\n俾美國國會順利表決通過條人權法<br />\n<br />\n香港就快死啦<br />\n一齊撐住好唔好<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n洗版洗到有組織搞9月9罷課為止</span></span>"},{"pid":"3bbdb8e1ef3c70b912859e51e5ac85bec3c60d54","tid":1541161,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"國會法案一日過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最快都要九月底"},{"pid":"