1,"uid":40147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"香港人唔該幫我簽晒佢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【白宮聯署 - 更新 05.09.2019 】<br />\n白宮死網近一星期，其實多咗好多新聯署，我頭先大約睇咗內容，頗多已經同之前的重複，所以我認為先推以下。其他我稍後再仔細睇睇，或再update。<br />\n1/ 白宮網常被攻擊，簽後久未收到電郵實屬正常，莫慌張，靜等候。<br />\n2/ 唔肯定簽咗未嘅，簽多一次。呢個情況可以接受，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n3/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n4/ 先分享＞回來簽署＞等電郵＞確認簽署<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名（重新出）<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NDIpyv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NDIpyv&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=baeba3f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NDIpyv</a><br />\n<br />\n請通過《香港人權及民主法案》，追究香港警察性暴力（重新出）<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UhvZgJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UhvZgJ&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=2e716c85\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UhvZgJ</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政府及警察策動831太子恐怖襲擊，請美國予以制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LaS51A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LaS51A&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=14d2f660\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LaS51A</a><br />\n<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=f67cdb33\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=cce033f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=47745183\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=25288225\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=b29d1eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n《以下夠數，但到期前越多人越好》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=54a981c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=652d0d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZbGdQH&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=9c4a7bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/archuoic/posts/384266258826189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Farchuoic%2Fposts%2F384266258826189&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=2f3f65f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/archuoic/posts/384266258826189</a>"},{"pid":"b14139aff7b4d12a57b386978c4f5c37540825bd","tid":1541161,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"9月8唔係復會咩？之後又要聽證會又要傾details 真係落實可能10